The Police in Ogun State have arrested the pastor in charge of Spirit Filled International Christian Church, Olumore, Abeokuta, Pastor Timothy Oluwatimilehin, for raping a housewife and her two daughters. The suspect allegedly lured the woman and the daughters away from her husband’s home and kept them in his own house and constantly had sex with them. The pastor was arrested following a complaint at the Adatan Police Station by the husband of the victim, who was accompanied by an official of the Ministry of Women Affairs. The police spokesman in the state, Abimbola Oyeyemi, told newsmen on Thursday that, “On interrogation, the pastor confessed to the commission of the crime and pleaded forgiveness. In his confession, he explained that he took advantage of a little misunderstanding between the woman and her husband to carry out the devilish act.”